title: Phantom 2040.m4v
description:
This hour and a half movie is essentially a clip show of what I believe to be the first story arc of the very cool Phantom 2040 cartoon series from the mid 90s.

While Peter Chung is credited with the design, I feel he may have been more of an art director in collaboration with other animators, specifically Thom Schillinger.
